# Link to this sectionWorkouts Monitoring using Ultralytics YOLO26#

[![Open Workouts Monitoring In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/ultralytics/notebooks/blob/main/notebooks/how-to-monitor-workouts-using-ultralytics-yolo.ipynb)

